▶️  Steps for creating a custom wamv configuration

➡️ Step 1
cd ~/vrx_ws/src/my_wamv

➡️ Step 2
Create thruster_config.yaml and component_config.yaml files with the required content

➡️ Step 3 
Run the following command in terminal in the same folder where the above two files are present

"ros2 launch vrx_gazebo generate_wamv.launch.py component_yaml:=`pwd`/component_config.yaml thruster_yaml:=`pwd`/thruster_config.yaml wamv_target:=`pwd`/wamv_target.urdf wamv_locked:=False"

➡️ Step 4
The previous command will generate 2 xacro files and 1 urdf file
      1️⃣️ component_config.xacro
      2️⃣️ thruster_config.xacro
      
      3️⃣️ wamv_target.urdf





